
Ranger Help for: camoflage (camo)
=================================

SYNTAX:      camoflage/camoflage <target>
USAGE:       forest,plains,swamp,desert,jungle,hills,road,beach,
             mountain,arctic,barren,outside,underground
SLOT COST:   11
BASE SP:     35 sp
SKILL TYPE:  defensive

SUMMARY:    
This skill allows a Ranger to conceal him or herself in the surrounding
terrain. A Ranger can also conceal other players as well. Any concealed
player will remain concealed until they perform any action besides:
(look,users,sc,hp,inv,i,inventory,who,rangers,ran or eran). Any commands
besides the ones listed here will cause the player to become unconcealed.
A concealed player is invisible to all players except for Rangers that
have a higher wisdom and wizards+. 

